      {
        "question": "Is this safe to use on company computers?",
        "answer": "Yes, the toolkit creates image files locally with no network access beyond standard Python libraries."
      },
      {
        "question": "My GIF is over the size limit. How do I fix it?",
        "answer": "Reduce frame count, lower color depth, simplify animations, or decrease dimensions. Suggestions provided."
      },
      {
        "question": "How does this compare to online GIF makers?",
        "answer": "This toolkit gives precise control over Slack requirements and creates files that meet exact constraints."
